<view class="page">
  <view class="status-bar" style="height: {{statusBarHeight}}px"></view>
  <view class="nav">
    <view class="back-btn" bindtap="onBackTap">◀</view>
    <text class="title">骑手登录</text>
  </view>

  <view class="content">
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">手机号</text>
      <input class="input" type="number" maxlength="11" placeholder="请输入注册手机号" bindinput="onPhoneInput" value="{{phone}}" />
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">验证码</text>
      <view class="code-row">
        <input class="input" placeholder="请输入短信验证码" bindinput="onCodeInput" value="{{code}}" />
        <view class="send-btn {{countdown>0 ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="onSendCode">
          {{countdown>0 ? countdown + 's后重发' : '获取验证码'}}
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="tip">
      <view class="tip-item">• 暂未启用短信校验，直接点击“登录”即可进入骑手端</view>
      <view class="tip-item">• 登录后可进入接单页面管理配送任务</view>
    </view>

    <view class="btn primary" bindtap="onLogin">登录</view>
  </view>
</view>


